data.description: Welcome to your serene countryside retreat at 10500 Anderson Rd.! Nestled on 5 sprawling acres of picturesque landscape, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and comfort. Welcome to 10500 Anderson Rd., where comfort meets spaciousness in this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, thoughtfully designed living space. on a generous 5.03-acre lot, this property offers a perfect blend of serenity and modern living.  5.03 acres offer endless possibilities - from creating your own private oasis to potential expansion or recreational activities. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your haven
